JcQIyiT4RQ">Phụng tặng Tiên Vu kinh triệu nhị thập vận - 奉贈鮮于京兆二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/S%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-v%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%C3%A1p/poem-SK_y8wVucpWN9zKU-mphNw">Sư đệ vấn đáp - 師弟問答</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Y%E1%BA%BFt/Thi%E1%BA%BFu-ni%C3%AAn-h%C3%A0nh/poem-2vCQ_UomDAzk2lDUIQIMMQ">Thiếu niên hành - 少年行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Y%E1%BA%BFt/author-gbSc6SZFs9WJWOa-eGUrHg">Thiệu Yết</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/V%C3%A3n-t%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-c%C3%B4ng/poem-cDElVqf2JwRbA8T7Kf-a_A">Vãn tư đồ công - 輓司徒公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%E1%BB%A8c/author-KitWPFSrhqgQGR4JMcSBew">Nguyễn Ức</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-E7-Rf1yoyy23OFGW9jeWAQ">Xuân nhật hữu cảm kỳ 1 - 春日有感其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Quang-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-X3Oume1_mYQvTGcgMAhydQ">Trần Quang Khải</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
